The paper combines neural embedding models and logic-based modules to address the challenges of ontology alignment, which involves semantic matching and reasoning. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper deals with large datasets and proposes a method that can be integrated into existing systems, which suggests that it may also belong to the sub-categories of Databases (cs.DB) and Software Engineering (cs.SE).
